Context: User is logged in as an Admin or Project Manager on the management page

Primary Flow
	1. User selects the "Create Group" button.
	2. User enters new group details 
	3. System validates the input fields.
	4. If validation succeeds, the system creates the group in the database.
	5. System updates the group list to reflect the new entry.

ALT FLOWS
	4a. If validation fails, the system displays an error message and prompts the user to correct the input.